This is the Bug Presenter -- a tool for presenting information from Bugzilla
(primary Whiteboard information, for now)

Authors
-------

Created by Robinson Tryon <qubit@runcibility.com> - 2013


License
-------

This tool is licensed under the GNU General Public License, version
3. See individual files for license headers.


Documentation
-------------

Data for this Bug Presenter is pulled out of Bugzilla using the
following commands:


# UNCONFIRMED bugs
wget -O bugzilla-data_UNCONFIRMED.csv "https://bugs.freedesktop.org/buglist.cgi?bug_status=UNCONFIRMED&product=LibreOffice&query_format=advanced&limit=0&ctype=csv&human=1&columnlist=bug_id,product,component,assigned_to,bug_status,short_desc,op_sys,status_whiteboard,keywords"

# NEW, ASSIGNED, REOPENED bugs
wget -O bugzilla-data_NEW-ASSIGNED-REOPENED.csv "https://bugs.freedesktop.org/buglist.cgi?bug_status=NEW&bug_status=ASSIGNED&bug_status=REOPENED&product=LibreOffice&query_format=advanced&limit=0&ctype=csv&human=1&columnlist=bug_id,product,component,assigned_to,bug_status,short_desc,op_sys,status_whiteboard,keywords"
